# Layer boundaries

## Import rules

- `app/` **never** imports from `server/` (directly or via `@/server/...`).
- Shared contracts live in `shared/` (HTTP helpers, Oshima schemas, quadkeys).
- Browser HTTP clients live in `app/adapter/` (not `server/adapter/`).
- `server/adapter/*-route.ts` is Worker/upstream only.
- Enforce with `bun run check:boundaries`.

## Data flow

```
container ← usecase mapper (domain → container shape)
    ↑
usecase   ← calls repository only
    ↑
repository ← wraps adapter + repository mapper (wire → domain)
    ↑
app/adapter or shared
```

Both `usecase/` and `repository/` may own their own mapper when shapes differ. Do not map container shapes inside adapters or repositories beyond domain, and do not call repositories from components.
